## Updated .gitignore – Copy and Replace

```gitignore
# Compiled files
*.class
target/

# IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.settings/
.project
.classpath

# Log files
*.log

# CSV data files (user data, not code)
accounts.csv
transactions.csv
system_config.txt

# Maven
pom.xml.tag
pom.xml.releaseBackup
pom.xml.versionsBackup
pom.xml.next
release.properties
dependency-reduced-pom.xml
buildNumber.properties
.mvn/timing.properties